snippet.title: Battlefield 1 Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
'The very definition of a modern shooter' - Eurogamer.net

It's time to experience war on an epic scale. It's time to destroy massive airships and take part in thrilling cavalry charges. It's time to play Battlefield 1.

Subscribe and be the first to see BF1 trailers and videos: http://bit.ly/270eMcA

“Seven Nation Army” by The White Stripes (The Glitch Mob Remix) - http://smarturl.it/SevenNationArmy
